---
import { BookOpen, Church, Heart } from "@lucide/astro"

const pillarIconClass =
	"mx-auto h-8 w-8 shrink-0 text-(--campaign-gold) sm:h-8 sm:w-8 md:mx-0"
const pillarLabelClass =
	"mt-2 font-bebas text-[1.2rem] leading-tight tracking-[0.04em] text-(--campaign-navy) sm:mt-3 sm:text-md sm:tracking-wide md:text-[1.35rem] md:leading-none md:tracking-[0.06em]"
---

<section
	class="uncorazon-vision reveal relative z-10 px-5 py-20 pb-24 sm:py-24 sm:pb-28"
	aria-labelledby="uncorazon-vision-heading">
	<div
		class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden"
		aria-hidden="true">
		<svg
			class="uncorazon-vision__house-watermark"
			viewBox="0 0 240 220"
			fill="currentColor">
			<path d="M120 205 15 85 50 28 120 98 190 28 225 85 120 205Z"></path>
		</svg>
		<svg
			class="uncorazon-vision__house-heart-watermark"
			viewBox="0 0 240 220"
			fill="currentColor"
			aria-hidden="true">
			<path
				fill-rule="evenodd"
				d="M40 205 40 100 120 20 200 100 200 205ZM120 175 85 140 105 115 120 125 135 115 155 140Z"
			></path>
		</svg>
	</div>

	<div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl">
		<header class="mb-10 text-center sm:mb-12">
			<div
				class="mb-4 flex justify-center text-(--campaign-gold)"
				aria-hidden="true">
				<svg
					class="h-12 w-12 sm:h-14 sm:w-14"
					viewBox="0 0 240 220"
					fill="currentColor">
					<path
						d="M120 205 15 85 50 28 120 98 190 28 225 85 120 205Z"
					></path>
				</svg>
			</div>
			<h2
				id="uncorazon-vision-heading"
				class="font-bebas text-4xl tracking-[0.02em] text-(--campaign-navy) sm:text-5xl">
				La Visión
			</h2>
		</header>

		<div
			class="uncorazon-vision__body space-y-6 text-[1.25rem] leading-[1.75] text-(--campaign-navy)/90">
			<p>
				<strong class="font-semibold text-(--campaign-navy)"
					>Un Corazón para Su Casa</strong
				>
				es la visión de levantar un espacio donde nuestra iglesia
				pueda vivir plenamente su propósito:
				<span class="uncorazon-vision__highlight"
					>amar a Dios, amar a la familia y amar al servicio</span
				>.
			</p>
			<p>
				Este nuevo edificio será un lugar donde todos se
				conecten con Dios, las familias sean fortalecidas y cada
				persona pueda encontrar libertad, descubrir su propósito
				y vivir su llamado para servir a Dios.
			</p>
			<p>
				Además, será el hogar de nuestro colegio cristiano,
				Murphy Christian Academy, donde formaremos a niños y
				jóvenes con principios bíblicos, desarrollando su fe,
				carácter y propósito para impactar el mundo.
			</p>
			<p class="mb-0">
				Este proyecto no es solo para hoy, es para el futuro.
				Estamos construyendo un lugar que servirá a las próximas
				generaciones y dejará un legado espiritual, familiar y
				educativo.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div
			class="mt-14 border-t border-(--campaign-navy)/10 pt-12"
			role="list">
			<div
				class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-x-2 sm:gap-x-4 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1px_1fr_1px_1fr] md:items-start md:gap-x-6 md:gap-y-0 lg:gap-x-10">
				<div
					class="min-w-0 text-center md:text-left"
					role="listitem">
					<Church
						class={pillarIconClass}
						stroke-width={1.5}
						aria-hidden="true"
					/>
					<p class={pillarLabelClass}>Adoración</p>
				</div>
				<div
					class="hidden min-h-18 w-px justify-self-center bg-(--campaign-gold)/45 md:block"
					role="presentation"
					aria-hidden="true">
				</div>
				<div
					class="min-w-0 text-center md:text-left"
					role="listitem">
					<Heart
						class={pillarIconClass}
						stroke-width={1.5}
						aria-hidden="true"
					/>
					<p class={pillarLabelClass}>Familia</p>
				</div>
				<div
					class="hidden min-h-18 w-px justify-self-center bg-(--campaign-gold)/45 md:block"
					role="presentation"
					aria-hidden="true">
				</div>
				<div
					class="min-w-0 text-center md:text-left"
					role="listitem">
					<BookOpen
						class={pillarIconClass}
						stroke-width={1.5}
						aria-hidden="true"
					/>
					<p
						class:list={[
							pillarLabelClass,
							"text-balance",
						]}>
						Educación
						<span
							class="mt-1 block font-[Cormorant_Garamond,serif] text-[0.75rem] font-normal italic leading-snug text-(--campaign-navy)/70 sm:text-sm md:text-sm">
							Murphy Christian Academy
						</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.uncorazon-vision {
		background-color: var(--campaign-cream);
		background-image: radial-gradient(
			ellipse 85% 55% at 50% 0%,
			var(--campaign-gold-soft) 0%,
			transparent 62%
		);
	}

	.uncorazon-vision__house-watermark {
		position: absolute;
		left: 50%;
		top: 38%;
		width: min(110vw, 720px);
		max-width: none;
		height: auto;
		translate: -50% -50%;
		rotate: -10deg;
		color: var(--campaign-navy);
		opacity: 0.09;
		-webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(
			ellipse 58% 52% at 50% 48%,
			#000 18%,
			transparent 72%
		);
		mask-image: radial-gradient(
			ellipse 58% 52% at 50% 48%,
			#000 18%,
			transparent 72%
		);
	}

	.uncorazon-vision__house-heart-watermark {
		position: absolute;
		right: max(-4%, calc(50% - 50rem));
		top: 4%;
		width: min(42vw, 240px);
		max-width: none;
		height: auto;
		translate: 18% -8%;
		rotate: -10deg;
		color: var(--campaign-navy);
		opacity: 0.3;
		-webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(
			ellipse 52% 48% at 58% 42%,
			#000 16%,
			transparent 70%
		);
		mask-image: radial-gradient(
			ellipse 52% 48% at 58% 42%,
			#000 16%,
			transparent 70%
		);
	}

	@media (min-width: 1024px) {
		.uncorazon-vision__house-heart-watermark {
			right: max(2%, calc(50% - 26rem));
			top: 6%;
			width: min(28vw, 260px);
		}
	}

	.uncorazon-vision__body {
		font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.uncorazon-vision__highlight {
		box-decoration-break: clone;
		-webkit-box-decoration-break: clone;
		border-bottom: 2px solid var(--campaign-gold);
		padding-bottom: 1px;
	}

	.uncorazon-vision.reveal {
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translate3d(0, 28px, 0);
		transition:
			opacity 0.85s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1),
			transform 0.85s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
	}

	.uncorazon-vision.reveal.visible {
		opacity: 1;
		transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
	}

	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
		.uncorazon-vision.reveal {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: none;
			transition: none;
		}
	}
</style>
